org.batfish.datamodel.answers

Class AclLines2Rows

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.answers.AclLines2Rows
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AclLinesAnswerElementInterface

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public class AclLines2Rows
extends java.lang.Object
implements AclLinesAnswerElementInterface
    Represents answers to aclReachability2. Implements AclLinesAnswerElementInterface so that aclReachability and aclReachability2 can use some of the same methods to answer both.
